comments: Beverley (PHI) is not established in a legal guarding position in Brown's (BOS) path when contact occurs that affects his SQBR.
Brown (BOS) reaches in and makes contact with the ball and marginal contact occurs with Covington's (PHI) right shoulder.
Bamba (PHI) establishes himself in Pritchard's (BOS) path and marginal contact occurs as the two come together during the pick.
Holiday (BOS) is moving alongside Beverley's (PHI) path and marginal body contact occurs during Beverley's drive to the basket.
Covington (PHI) spins into Holiday (BOS) and dislodges him from his legal guarding position.
Brown (BOS) establishes himself in Covington's (PHI) path and marginal contact occurs to Covington's shoulder as Brown slips by.
Horford (BOS) establishes himself in Covington's (PHI) path and slightly extends his bent arm to Covington's side as he defends over the screen.
Although Beverley (PHI) makes contact with the ball, in order to get to the ball he initiates illegal contact with Holiday's (BOS) arm that causes him to lose control of the ball.
Covington (PHI) brings his hands toward Pritchard (BOS) and marginal contact occurs as Covington releases away.
Bamba (PHI) reaches in and makes contact with the ball and any contact with White's (BOS) hand is incidental.
Covington (PHI) contests the layup attempt and marginal body contact occurs with Pritchard (BOS) after the release.
Bamba (PHI) hands off the ball in Brown's (BOS) path and absorbs the contact.
Pritchard (BOS) legally contests Morris Sr.'s (PHI) jump shot attempt.
Beverley (PHI) commits a take foul on Horford (BOS).
Pritchard (BOS) briefly places a hand on Beverley's (PHI) arm and the contact does not affect his FOM.
Bamba (PHI) establishes himself in White's (BOS) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Brown (BOS) commits a take foul on Harris (PHI).
Morris Sr. (PHI) and Horford (BOS) mutually engage and immediately disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Bamba (PHI) brushes Kornet's (BOS) arm after Kornet gathers the loose ball.
